rations.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mrz 2024) 0aCivil-military relationszColombia. 0aDemocracyzColombia. 4aPolitics and Law : International Relations. 7aPOLITICAL SCIENCE / International Relations / General.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9780791482049?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780791482049423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780791482049/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles